(x_i, y_i), i = 1, 2, \ldots n,
 {\textit mean}(x) = \frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n x_i 
 {\textit var}(x) = \frac{1}{n-1}\sum_{i=1}^n (x_i - {\textit mean}(x))^2 
 {\textit cov}(x,y)  = \frac{1}{n-1}\sum_{i=1}^n (x_i - {\textit mean}(x))(y_i - {\textit mean}(y)). 
